metadata.title: Remix Me - Dynamic Token
metadata.name: Remix Me - Dynamic Token
metadata.description:
The spell is broken. Now, you can all see clearly. Welcome to the WEB3, a place where it is possible to collaborate, co-create, and remix each other. Welcome to the world of freedom; we were waiting for you. 
Look in the eyes of the fairy and say the magic words: de-central-ize. 
 
Remix of Remixes #3, by Hackatao, is the last stop - before the ultimate Remix of all the remixes of the remixes - of this exciting art project that called for artists to participate in the "remixing activities." The result of a melting pot of styles, personalities, and ideas. 
 
This is a snapshot of the third Remix of remixes, that crystallizes the look of the dynamic token in this precise moment until the following change. 
Twelve artists and twelve works are finely (re)mixed by Hackatao, each contributing to the final unique creation, existing between balance and harmony and finding its rhythm in the music of MaterManto
 
We are approaching "the end," and she (the Goddess of Justice) is now a magic fairy. Don't worry. If you've got here, it means that you are very awake! In fact, you won a ticket to WEB3. 
Find out about the project: https://hackatao.com/remixme
